<aside class="seatmap-side seatmap-side--left stage4-left">
    <div class="seatmap-side__title">STEP 04 · 좌석 배치</div>

    <div class="seatmap-step-list">
        <section id="part1Panel" class="seatmap-step is-active" data-step="1">
            <button type="button" class="seatmap-step__header active" id="partBtn1">
                <span class="seatmap-step__check" data-step="1"></span>
                <span class="seatmap-step__text">
                    <b>파트 1</b>
                    <small>구역 펼쳐보기 · 회전</small>
                </span>
                <span class="seatmap-step__status" id="part1Status">진행중</span>
                <span class="seatmap-step__arrow">⌄</span>
            </button>

            <div class="seatmap-step__body">
                <div class="seatmap-step__system">
                    <div class="box active">
                        <h3>seatmap-sections.json 기준</h3>
                        <div class="help-text">
                            Stage 3에서 확정한 구역 polygon을 원본 도면 위에 억지로 찍지 않고, 작업판에 구역 카드처럼 펼쳐서 배치합니다. 여기서 좌석을 넣으면 실제 예매 구역 크기가 확정됩니다.
                        </div>

                        <div class="row">
                            <div>
                                <label for="groupFilter">그룹 필터</label>
                                <select id="groupFilter"></select>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <label for="sectionSelect">선택 구역</label>
                                <select id="sectionSelect"></select>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <input id="sectionSearch" class="stage4-search" placeholder="구역명 검색: A1, D2, VIP" />
                        <div class="section-list stage4-section-list" id="sectionList"></div>

                        <div class="stage4-rotate-box">
                            <label for="angleInput">선택 구역 회전</label>
                            <div class="stage4-rotate-controls">
                                <button type="button" class="btn" id="rotateLeftBtn">↺ -15°</button>
                                <input id="angleInput" type="number" min="-180" max="180" step="1" value="0" />
                                <button type="button" class="btn" id="rotateRightBtn">↻ +15°</button>
                            </div>
                            <div class="help-text">각 구역 도형 위쪽 회전점을 드래그해도 됩니다. 좌석 방향이 애매한 정사각형 구역은 여기서 먼저 반듯하게 맞춥니다.</div>
                        </div>

                        <button type="button" class="btn primary" id="goPart2Btn">다음: 구역별 좌석 추정</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="part2Panel" class="seatmap-step" data-step="2">
            <button type="button" class="seatmap-step__header" id="partBtn2">
                <span class="seatmap-step__check" data-step="2"></span>
                <span class="seatmap-step__text">
                    <b>파트 2</b>
                    <small>구역별 좌석 추정</small>
                </span>
                <span class="seatmap-step__status" id="part2Status">대기</span>
                <span class="seatmap-step__arrow">⌄</span>
            </button>

            <div class="seatmap-step__body">
                <div class="seatmap-step__system">
                    <div class="box active">
                        <h3>선택 구역 좌석 추정 / 실제 크기 다듬기</h3>
                        <div class="stage4-selected-name" id="selectedSectionName">구역을 선택하세요.</div>

                        <div class="row three">
                            <div>
                                <label for="rowsInput">행 수</label>
                                <input id="rowsInput" type="number" min="1" max="80" value="8" />
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <label for="colsInput">열 수</label>
                                <input id="colsInput" type="number" min="1" max="120" value="12" />
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="row three">
                            <div>
                                <label for="seatSizeInput">좌석 크기</label>
                                <input id="seatSizeInput" type="number" min="2" max="40" step="1" value="10" />
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <label for="gapXInput">가로 간격</label>
                                <input id="gapXInput" type="number" min="0" max="40" step="1" value="4" />
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <label for="gapYInput">세로 간격</label>
                                <input id="gapYInput" type="number" min="0" max="40" step="1" value="4" />
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="row">
                            <div>
                                <label for="rowStartInput">시작 행</label>
                                <input id="rowStartInput" value="A" maxlength="3" />
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <label for="colStartInput">시작 열</label>
                                <input id="colStartInput" type="number" min="1" max="999" value="1" />
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <button type="button" class="btn dark" id="generateSectionBtn">선택 구역 좌석 추정</button>
                        <button type="button" class="btn amber" id="inferAllBtn">전체 구역 자동 추정</button>
                        <button type="button" class="btn" id="tightenBoundsBtn">실제 구역 크기 재정리</button>
                        <button type="button" class="btn red" id="clearSectionBtn">선택 구역 좌석 비우기</button>
                        <div class="help-text">좌석 묶음 우하단 핸들을 드래그하면 좌석 크기와 실제 버튼 범위가 같이 커지거나 줄어듭니다.</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="part3Panel" class="seatmap-step" data-step="3">
            <button type="button" class="seatmap-step__header" id="partBtn3">
                <span class="seatmap-step__check" data-step="3"></span>
                <span class="seatmap-step__text">
                    <b>파트 3</b>
                    <small>최종 형태 검수 · 저장</small>
                </span>
                <span class="seatmap-step__status" id="part3Status">대기</span>
                <span class="seatmap-step__arrow">⌄</span>
            </button>

            <div class="seatmap-step__body">
                <div class="seatmap-step__system">
                    <div class="box active">
                        <h3>최종 형태 검수 · 좌석 추가/삭제</h3>
                        <div class="help-text">
                            좌석 클릭 = 선택, Shift + 클릭 = 다중 선택입니다. 여기서 구역별 좌석을 추가/삭제하고 최종 형태를 확정합니다.
                        </div>

                        <div class="row">
                            <div>
                                <label for="manualRowInput">수동 행</label>
                                <input id="manualRowInput" value="A" maxlength="3" />
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <label for="manualColInput">수동 열</label>
                                <input id="manualColInput" type="number" min="1" max="999" value="1" />
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <button type="button" class="btn" id="manualAddBtn">수동 좌석 추가 모드</button>
                        <button type="button" class="btn red" id="deleteSeatBtn">선택 좌석 삭제</button>
                        <button type="button" class="btn" id="clearSelectionBtn">좌석 선택 해제</button>
                    </div>

                    <div class="box">
                        <h3>검증 / 저장</h3>
                        <div class="stage4-save-summary" id="saveSummary">저장할 좌석 0개</div>
                        <button type="button" class="btn green" id="saveSeatsBtn">좌석 ID / 실제 구역 저장</button>
                        <button type="button" class="btn primary" id="toStage5Btn">Stage 5 예매 버튼 생성으로 이동</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</aside>

<main class="seatmap-main stage4-main" id="canvasScroll">
    <div class="canvas-wrap stage4-canvas-wrap">
        <span id="canvasTitle" class="sr-only">구역 펼쳐보기 좌석 배치 작업판</span>
        <span id="canvasSize" class="sr-only">-</span>
        <div class="canvas-box stage4-canvas-box" id="canvasBox">
            <canvas class="base" id="canvas"></canvas>
            <canvas id="overlay"></canvas>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>

<aside class="seatmap-side seatmap-side--right stage4-right">
    <div class="minimap">
        <h3>기준 도면</h3>
        <img id="miniImg" alt="기준 도면 미니맵" />
        <div class="help">미니맵은 button-image.png 확인용입니다. 중앙 작업판은 seatmap-sections.json의 polygon을 펼쳐서 표시합니다.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="preview-card stage4-info-card">
        <h3>선택 정보</h3>
        <dl class="stage4-info-list">
            <div><dt>구역</dt><dd id="infoSection">-</dd></div>
            <div><dt>sectionId</dt><dd id="infoSectionId">-</dd></div>
            <div><dt>층 / 등급</dt><dd id="infoFloorGrade">-</dd></div>
            <div><dt>가격</dt><dd id="infoPrice">-</dd></div>
            <div><dt>구역 좌석</dt><dd id="infoSectionSeats">0</dd></div>
            <div><dt>선택 좌석</dt><dd id="infoSelectedSeats">0</dd></div>
        </dl>
    </div>

    <div class="preview-card stage4-info-card">
        <h3>전체 현황</h3>
        <div class="stats">
            <div class="stat"><b id="totalSections">0</b><span>구역</span></div>
            <div class="stat"><b id="totalSeats">0</b><span>좌석</span></div>
        </div>
        <pre class="json-box stage4-json-preview" id="jsonPreview">[]</pre>
    </div>
</aside>
